title: Bikewatching Visualization
description: Interactive bike sharing visualization that allows users to filter by time and analyze patterns of bike departures and arrivals across the network.

title: Power Outage Analysis
description: Explored a dataset that recorded major power outages in the U.S. In particular we tried to answer: What is the relationship between the different classifications of regions, namely states and climate region, and the average outage duration?

title: Predicting Course Availability in First/Second Pass Enrollment at UCSD
description: This project addresses a major challenge for UCSD students: deciding which classes to enroll in during first and second pass

title: An Expository Visualisation on Grocery Store Foods
description: Created a visualisation exploring the GroceryDB dataset. In particular I answered the question: 'When supermarkets market private‑label lines as “healthy” alternatives, do those store brands actually contain fewer ultra‑processed items than their national‑brand equivalents?'
